{
  "stem": "17001.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 199.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And later on, when it got to be '44, then they made an announcement.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Those days they had a drummer who would walk on the middle of the street and he would start to drum.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Now, when he started to drum, then all the people would stand front of their gate or front of their house door and they listened.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And he had a paper in his hand and he would read, 'hear, hear, hear, the government of Hungary' and so and so.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He was phrasing it with such a flowery language that you would think that God now is-- and the Israelite people are not allowed to go on the street without a yellow star and they-- they're not allowed to travel and they're not allowed to go out after dark and so and so.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This took place in the end of-- end of '43, like the end of '43, the beginning of '44.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So we had some yellow material and we cut out some stars.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were having fun sewing it on our coat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you were supposed to have it on your dress also, but we didn't put it on our dress, because being that it was cold, you needed a coat, so you weren't walking around without a dress.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So that was just the beginning of it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then later on, they announced that-- that no Jews are allowed to leave their house.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were inside in the house, and we were looking through the gate.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were looking through the window behind the curtains.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had seen that there were this-- a lot of policemen, the gendarmes, they were going from each Jewish house.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
